    "body": "@Haroenv createURL from the usePagination hook is not starting at 0 but at 1.\r\n\r\nFor example:\r\n\r\n```\r\nconst { canRefine, pages, refine } = usePagination(props);\r\n\r\ncreateURL(0) => Gives another url as refine(0)\r\ncreateURL(1) => Gives another url as refine(1)\r\n\r\n```",
